data.description: Welcome home! Discover this charming 3-bedroom 2-bath home situated on the Northside of Jax. Enjoy the serenity of the Dinsmore Farms neighborhood. This home sits on just under a half-acre, providing you with large fenced in backyard and covered patios in both the front and rear of the home.  As you enter, you are greeted with a large kitchen and living area to make your own.  No HOA or CDD. Plenty of space for RV and boat storage. Conveniently located near JAX International and Northside amenities.  New HVAC installed 2020. Home is being sold AS-IS.
